{"title":"邵洪生","authors":["管桦"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"邵洪生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管桦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"………………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庆祝我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的新国家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象一朵花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的血汗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把她养育大！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——歌曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打了一夜零半天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗还没完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人缩进地堡里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扇形火网盖地皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地势开阔上不去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突击部队好着急。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员队前一声喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁把地堡去炸翻？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳出个战士吼一声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这个任务我完成！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众人一看是老邵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的名字都知道；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那天诉苦会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲的人人都落泪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邵洪生一生好命苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小没穿过一丝儿布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终朝每日光屁股。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天雪花落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱着胳臂打哆嗦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊月滴水成冰霜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒郊野外放牛羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手脚冻成疮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去找地主讨件衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦苦哀求不答理："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫一声大爷不吱声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫两声大爷变了脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骂声狗日的少纠缠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冻死不过臭块地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大爷有钱再雇去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挨打挨骂受折磨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半辈子泡在眼泪里过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉苦会上老邵讲的清："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“苦是地主给，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦从老蒋生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主老蒋一条根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔了这条根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷苦人民大翻身。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不知头一仗别人立了功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老邵瞅着早眼红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不知老邵有事蹩在心里头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党员去开会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老邵心难受；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么人家也是一个脑袋两只"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就不能够？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这次不把地堡连根掀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我老邵革命算白干！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大枪子弹全卸了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绑好鞋带紧紧腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急忙动手捆炸药，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划根火柴点着绳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹一点红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机枪步枪连声叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掩护老邵送炸药。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老邵窜到街当中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猫腰向前冲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下生了风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏过鹿柴哗啦啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飕飕子弹如雨下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手榴弹吭吭扔出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸裂火花迷人眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"块块黄土往上翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老邵心如铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老邵心如钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛着炸药向上闯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哇哇哇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机枪扫过来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老邵没躲开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸药变了一座山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重重压在肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下断了根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身子立不稳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两眼忽忽冒金花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打个“裂斜”倒地下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突击部队手握枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但等炸药一声响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人唉呀叫一声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫非敌人打死了邵洪生？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团团围住指导员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争着把雷点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胳臂举起象树林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员不知派谁人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然有人叫声道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老邵同志还活着！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邵洪生一阵昏迷一阵醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肚子打了个大窟窿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子弹搅的肚子痛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全身血染红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬紧牙根不出声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两脚拼命向后蹬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胳臂肘子柱着地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一步爬上去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬一截脑袋忽悠悠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬两截血汗满地流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好个战士邵洪生！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬到两个枪眼正当中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸药堆上地堡顶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬牙去点引火线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引火点着向回转。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背后轰隆隆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地堡腾上空！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砖石飞舞起浪烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地堡连根掀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员抱起邵洪生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听他朦胧叫一声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的任务已完成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说完这句话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千呼万唤不答声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从这日起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邵洪生的英名处处传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪念邵洪生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东奖章挂家中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军区记他三大功。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邵洪生名字写上英雄榜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邵洪生名字传遍城镇和村庄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"…………。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年，十、十三改作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）“裂斜”东北土话，即歪倒。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}